<div class="petitionContainer colCenter">
    <div class="petitionWrapper">

        <h1 class="petitionHeader fadeIn ">Brexit</h1>
        <h3 class="petitionSubHeader fadeIn midDelay"><strong>{ </strong>Pronunciation. Brit/'breksit/'<strong> }</strong></h3>

        <p class="petitionBody fadeIn delayOne">Let’s face it, we’re all sick of hearing about it, not just the reality of Brexit, which appears to be dragging on ad infinitum but it’s the word itself that still permeates all matters British and European alike at the minute. Unfortunately, it appears we cannot currently reverse the madness of the act that this indelibly horrific term embodies, but we could make strides towards consigning this abomination into the swear jar of history, by taking strides towards removing it from the </br><a id="oxford" target="_blank" href="https://www.oxfordmail.co.uk/news/14968256.brexit-added-to-the-oxford-english-dictionary/">Oxford english Dictionary.</a>
        <h3 class="petitionSubHeader fadeIn delayTwo">Please, sign below to help us <span>brextricate, brextract & brexpunge </span>Brexit from the <span>brexicon</span> of everyday life. </br></br></h3>
        {{#unless loggedin}}
            <p class="error_alert hide fadeIn delayFour">Register below, {{first}} to support our cause></p><a class="mainButton hide fadeIn delayFive" href="/registration">Register here</a>


        {{/unless}}

        {{#if loggedin}}
            <form id="petitionFormField" class="hide fadeIn delayFour" method="POST">
                <div class="canvasField">
                    <input id="signatureField" type="hidden" list="input" autocomplete="off" name="signature"></input>
                    <canvas id="signatureCanvas" width="380" height="200"></canvas>
                </div>
                <input name="_csrf" type="hidden" value="{{csrfToken}}">
                <div class="buttonContainer hide fadeIn delayFive">
                    <button class="mainButton">Submit</button>
                    <div class="mainButton" id="canvasClear">clear</div>
                </div>
            </form>
        {{/if}}
    </div>


{{#if error}}
    <p class="error_alert">{{error}}</p>
{{/if}}
</div>
